title: Hernandez replaces Joc for LA; Conforto in for Mets (Los Angeles Dodgers)
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Dodgers ) Mattingly replaced Joc Pederson in center field with Enrique Hernandez batting eighth, moved fellow rookie shortstop Corey Seager up from third in the order to second, had veteran Howie Kendrick leading off,
